{"tid":964026,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡1月1日起　提高合法吸煙年齡至19歲","createTime":"2019-01-01T03:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T16:51:07.000Z","uid":20058,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"68779a9f20455de353cb214ec279b1bb61bdbae5","tid":964026,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T03:36:23.000Z","msg":"新加坡在2019年1月1日起，將合法購買及吸煙最低年齡由18歲提高至19歲，隨後在2020年至2021年，逐步將年齡提高至20歲及21歲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新加坡2017年11月通過修正法案，合法吸煙年齡會在2019至2021年3年內，逐漸提高至21歲。新加坡衛生部表示，新法案目的是限制青少年接觸煙草製品，避免他們將吸煙「正常化」。<br />\n<br />\n根據煙草法（廣告及銷售限制），未滿法定年齡人士，不得購買、使用、擁有、出售或供應煙草製品。未滿法定年齡人士違反此法，最高罰款為300坡元（約1718港元）；零售商如向未滿法定年齡人士提供煙品，一經定罪，最高罰款為1萬坡元（約5.7萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n（馬來時報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20181230/s00005/1546179578321/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A11%E6%9C%881%E6%97%A5%E8%B5%B7-%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E5%90%B8%E7%85%99%E5%B9%B4%E9%BD%A1%E8%87%B319%E6%AD%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20181230%2Fs00005%2F1546179578321%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A11%25E6%259C%25881%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25B5%25B7-%25E6%258F%2590%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2590%25B8%25E7%2585%2599%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%25BD%25A1%25E8%2587%25B319%25E6%25AD%25B2&d=HoBoMebGnLthbdL9qGoKX5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=ab5c7762\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20181230%2Fs00005%2F1546179578321%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A11%25E6%259C%25881%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25B5%25B7-%25E6%258F%2590%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2590%25B8%25E7%2585%2599%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%25BD%25A1%25E8%2587%25B319%25E6%25AD%25B2&h=40ce7788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20181230/s00005/1546179578321/%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A11%E6%